item.title: CVE-2019-14863|2024-08-05T00:26:39.196Z -- red%20hat -- angular%3A
item.description: There is a vulnerability in all angular versions before 1.5.0-beta.0, where after escaping the context of the web application, the web application delivers data to its users along with other trusted dynamic content, without validating it.
